## 2026-04-04 - Consolidate duplicated Variable/Style sync code
- Created `useSyncEntity<TRow, TSnapshot>` generic hook that replaces both `useVariableSync` and `useStyleSync`. Takes two configs: static `SyncMessages` (message types + stable extractors) and a dynamic config (entity-specific build functions, stored in a ref). Returns neutral property names (`rows`, `dirs`, `loading`, `syncing`, `progress`, `error`, `checked`, `syncCount`, `pushCount`, `pullCount`, `snapshot`, `reverting`, `revertError`, `revert`, `readFigmaTokens`).
- Created `SyncSubPanel` generic component that replaces both `VariableSyncSubPanel` and `StyleSyncSubPanel`. Parameterized by text props (`description`, `sectionLabel`, `previewAction`, `applyAction`, `inSyncMessage`, `notCheckedMessage`, `revertDescription`).
- Rewrote `PublishPanel.tsx` to use `useSyncEntity` directly twice (for variables and styles) with module-level static configs (`VAR_MESSAGES`, `STYLE_MESSAGES`) and pure helper functions. Replaced both `VariableSyncSubPanel` usage and the inline style sync code (150+ lines) with `SyncSubPanel`. Removed local duplicate `VarDiffRowItem` and `ValueCell` components.

