## 2026-04-04 - Server token-store.ts has no unit tests
- Created `packages/server/src/__tests__/token-store.test.ts` with 150 tests across 16 describe blocks, covering: set CRUD (create/delete/rename/clearAll/reorder), set metadata (description/collectionName/modeName), token CRUD (create/get/update/delete/deleteTokens), circular reference detection (self-ref, 2-step cycle, 3-step cycle, batch checks), token rename/move/copy with alias cascade updates, group operations (create/rename/move/copy/duplicate/reorder), batch operations (batchUpsertTokens with skip/overwrite/merge, batchUpdateTokens, batchRenameTokens, batchMoveTokens, batchCopyTokens), bulkRename (plain + regex), token resolution (resolveTokens/resolveToken), cross-set dependents (getDependents/getGroupDependents), searchTokens (q/type/has/value/desc/pagination qualifiers), generator ID helpers (findTokensByGeneratorId/deleteTokensByGeneratorId), restoreSnapshot, onChange events, disk persistence on initialize, pending-rename crash recovery, and beginBatch/endBatch deferred rebuild.
- Fixed 2 test failures: `ResolvedToken` uses `.$value` not `.resolvedValue`.
- Files changed: `packages/server/src/__tests__/token-store.test.ts` (new, 570 lines)

