## 2026-04-04 - Plugin sandbox fontLoading.ts cache poisoned by API errors
- Changed `cachedFonts: Font[] | null` to `cachedFontsPromise: Promise<Font[]> | null` so concurrent callers share the same in-flight request.
- On rejection, the `.catch` handler clears `cachedFontsPromise = null` so retries trigger a fresh API call.
- `getAvailableFonts()` is now synchronous (returns the cached/new Promise directly) rather than async, eliminating the redundant await.

